text: Cyclophorus elegans is a species of small, air-breathing, land snails with an operculum, terrestrial pulmonate gastropod molluscs in the family Cyclophoridae. It is found in China. == References == * Die chinesischen Land- und Subwasser-Gastropoden des Natur-Museums Senckenberg.
